plyTime":"2017-03-08T04:43:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴士有車cam<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好多巴士司機自己裝 （好似係"},{"pid":"bacfe82e09a2a7d648e05ec68336e53e49df7127","tid":147452,"uid":17405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T04:47:56.000Z","msg":"最撚慘就係d dc9永遠唔使停牌，扣3,5分又開工<br />\n<br />\n睇下比人放蛇d黑的，衰左幾次仲有得再衰，<br />\n<br />\n呢個政府不知所謂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5eef7e0addebd03dcafe9597d93ddaa6b6841ef","tid":147452,"uid":55597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T04:57:17.000Z","msg":"真係好撚戇鳩<br />\n講力量，的士一定唔夠巴士撞<br />\n講道德，巴士成車人屌你一個的士佬，又有車 cam，唔到你柒<br />\n講法律，的士咁切線一定犯法"}]}